{"tid":2370674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"AM Group Limited 扮pt轉介 呃人上去interview","createTime":"2021-01-18T08:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T12:24:44.000Z","uid":348873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"70ec6d99d43e38bd53005c5f92cb7925a2f71270","tid":2370674,"uid":348873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"話說琴日有知人打比我<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JS14dnU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJS14dnU.png&h=49b98b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話之前收到我application 約我上黎interview 話一陣wts 我 之後呢個人就聯絡我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FKJtWH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FKJtWH.png&h=5634cbd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢全部係錄音我 我心捻無啦啦約我interview？<br />\n咁我就越諗越唔對路 上網直接search佢電話 一搵就搵到呢啲咁嘅嘢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6y6rJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6y6rJQ.png&h=de717a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知佢有冇偷人圖 但大家小心<br />\n問佢我application入邊嘅email係咩 又兜好大個圈話想同你經理會答我 問D問題全部回避我 我淨係聯絡我做interview 咁你哋收到application先有我聯絡方式先聯絡到我㗎嘛 <br />\n<br />\n我：上網完全搵唔到你間公司 <br />\n佢：唔緊要，我將上次contact 你講既內容講多一次，我地呢邊係對內部門，所以唔會set up網址，而且同合作品牌有保密協議，所以對實際工作內容可以面試再問經理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司：AM Group Ltd. <br />\n地址：新輝商業中心 太子新填地街574-580號 <br />\n(旺角MTR Exit A2 步行10分鐘）<br />\n準備： <br />\n1.整齊衣著 （短褲拖鞋禁止）<br />\n2. 基本履歷 (CV) 中或英 亦可 <br />\n3. 學生證副本/証件相"},{"pid":"99750be5d618163dbff71056d6286b5f7d3926de","tid":2370674,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:10:29.000Z","msg":"正撚屌"},{"pid":"49f6f4b661e770e6e98d6e211036216acef0000e","tid":2370674,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"Company Name: <br />\nA.M. GROUP LIMITED<br />\n香港鴻鵠集團有限公司"},{"pid":"066bb83ca2eec0ef6c05f0d633b8cd65aa265504","tid":2370674,"uid":348873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49f6f4b661e770e6e98d6e211036216ac